          "reviewBody": "Excellence through endeavour - HUS has been true to its motto. Our two sons have been in HUS right from the beginning and their way of teaching has laid a solid foundation for the kids future. I’m sure the teachers invest a lot of time and effort into teaching the kids. A huge thanks to the teachers at Loko Poko and HUS - my younger son (who struggled a lot with reading and writing during COVID) is now confident with reading and writing. My children are extremely happy especially when they come back home and talk about everything they learned. HUS celebrates sports day, graduation day, various festivals and in-house arts and science programs with a lot of fun and fervour and all of us (including the children) truly enjoy it. We as parents are extremely satisfied and not worried about our children’s future when HUS provides the best learning experience for them.",
